Package cnc.ui

Package contains all classes belonging to the UI and it's functionality.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CoolingSimulator
    Class needed to simulate the cooling function on the UI.
    DrillPointer
    Class is needed to simulate the drill on the UI
    HomePoint
    Class for displaying HomePoint
    Main
    Main Class of JavaFx Application.
    SimulateMill
    Class for simulating the drilling of previously calculated coordinates coordinates have already been calculated in Drill
    UIController
    Class for controlling the user Interface of the cnc machine simulator Ui design is done using fxml
    WorkSurface
    Class for worksurface off CNC_Machine this is the drawing area
